Section: oldlibs
Depends: fonts-symbola, ${misc:Depends}
Description: symbolic font providing emoji chars from Unicode 9.0 (transit. pkg)
 This dummy package is provided for a smooth transition from the
 previous ttf-ancient-fonts-symbola package to the fonts-symbola package.
 .
 It may be safely removed after installation.

Package: fonts-symbola
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Breaks: ttf-ancient-fonts-symbola (<< 2.59)
Replaces: ttf-ancient-fonts-symbola (<< 2.59)
Provides: ttf-ancient-fonts-symbola
Description: symbolic font providing emoji characters from Unicode 9.0
 This package includes the Symbola font, which contains special symbols and
 emoji characters which are encoded in the Unicode Standard 9.0
